    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "b7c      At 10:45 PM on the evening of July 11, 1947, Clerk [REDACTED] of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Washington Field Office called and stated that at the instruction Mr.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Hennrich he wanted to pass on to the Bureau information he had just re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "ceived from one [REDACTED] Laurel, Maryland, to the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "effect that a \"flying disc\" had just landed in [REDACTED] yard \"and the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "machinery is still buzzing.\" [REDACTED] stated [REDACTED] was apparently so excited he had",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "a difficult time even getting his name out, and no further detail could be obtained",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "from him.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "b7c      At 10:50 PM I passed the above information on to [REDACTED] duty officer",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "at G-2 who indicated he had also received the same data from another source, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "would pass our information along to appropriate army quarters.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "b7c      [REDACTED] of the AP called at about 10:55 PM and asked whether the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Bureau had received any report on a \"flying disc\" in Laurel Maryland. After",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "checking with Mr. Nichols I told him we had received such a report and had passed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "it on to army authorities.",
      "status": "image_matched"
